      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOTSHOT LILY (1) boasts strong form at this track having won three times from four starts. Was out of placings last time (17.87) at Richmond Straight in a NG, finishing seventh and beaten 6 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. BEAR'S HEAD (7) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 2.5 lengths away in second (22.56). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from four attempts. Ready to find winning form. SIR TICK (5) turned in a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Mia Zipper (22.96) in a NG. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from six starts. Can measure up this time. PRINCE BERNARDO (8) bold run expected on best form.",
